  "body": "### Summary\r\n\r\n(too much space over switcher cards)\r\n<img src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/17097240/46db53de-8bd0-4ad4-8003-fa1fe80de9fc\" width=200/>\r\n\r\nWe do apply top margin to switcher cards, but for some reason status-bar also pushing cards down. So in a way margin gets double. But we can't remove manual applied margin, because push down by status bar is random, it usually happens on start of app. Not sure when it started to happen, might be related to rn upgrade.\r\n",
